    ITableImportAPI

    ITableImportAPIService  
    ITypelistToolsAPI
    ITypelistToolsAPI provides methods that allow for the extraction of typelist data from the system.
    ITypelistToolsAPIService  
    IUserAPI
    UserAPI is used to perform operations on users.
    IUserAPIService  
    IWorkflowAPI
    External API for performing operations on workflows.
    IWorkflowAPIService  
    IZoneImportAPI
    IZoneImportAPI is a remote interface to a set of tools to import zone data (in csv format) into the staging tables.
